# Generated build output and coverage are not source.
# These directories are slipping into the working tree because the workspace
# root .gitignore patterns (`dist/`, `coverage/`) match anchored entries that
# git applied before the tree was reorganized into packages/. A package-local
# .gitignore makes the intent explicit and survives any future restructuring.
#
# To untrack files already committed (do this manually, NOT via the emitter):
#   git rm -r --cached packages/typespec-zod/dist packages/typespec-zod/coverage
dist/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo
